        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer46739691" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17798606352558053483">Excellent book!!! I highly recommend this one. I think it&apos;s a great way to understand a little better the complexities of African beliefs and tribal life. It&apos;s not a &quot;religion&quot; to them, it&apos;s a way of life (believing everything has a spirit, for example).</span>
  <span id="freeText17798606352558053483" style="display:none">Excellent book!!! I highly recommend this one. I think it's a great way to understand a little better the complexities of African beliefs and tribal life. It's not a "religion" to them, it's a way of life (believing everything has a spirit, for example).</span>
