        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer591525792" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16153208969862684253">A story about a girl who is hated by her family and runs away to escape being force to marry. I think I would have enjoyed this better if I wasn&apos;t reading The Island of the Blue Dolphin with my daughter at the same time. I think the two together made for a little too much &quot;girl survives in the wild against all odds&quot; for my own tastes. That said I enjoyed the story and it made me really glad that I do not have to eat bugs in order to survive. And it had a pretty happy ending which is always nice.</span>
  <span id="freeText16153208969862684253" style="display:none">A story about a girl who is hated by her family and runs away to escape being force to marry. I think I would have enjoyed this better if I wasn't reading The Island of the Blue Dolphin with my daughter at the same time. I think the two together made for a little too much "girl survives in the wild against all odds" for my own tastes. That said I enjoyed the story and it made me really glad that I do not have to eat bugs in order to survive. And it had a pretty happy ending which is always nice.</span>
