            <span class="readable">&ldquo;I am she who lifts the mountains<br />When she goes to hunt,<br />Who wears mamba for a headband<br />And a lion for a belt.<br />Beware!<br />I swallow elephants whole<br />And pick my teeth with rhinoceros horns,<br />I drink up rivers to get at the hippos.<br />Let them hear my words!<br />Nhamo is coming<br />And her hunger is great.<br /><br />I am she who tosses trees<br />Instead of spears.<br />The ostrich is my pillow<br />And the elephant is my footstool!<br />I am Nhamo<br />Who makes the river my highway<br />And sends crocodiles scurrying into the reeds!&rdquo;</span>
